<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.6.11">
<l>kaṇkaḷ kāṇṭaṟ kariya ṉāykkarut tukku naṉṟume ḷiyaṉāy</l>
<l>maṇkoṇ ñālattu yirkkel lāmaruḷ ceyyum vāṉava rīcaṉaip</l>
<l>paṇkoḷ cōlai vaḻuti vaḷanāṭaṉ kurukaik kōṉcaṭa kōpaṉcol</l>
<l>paṇko ḷāyirat tippat tālpatta rākak kūṭum payilumiṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>With these ten in the melodious thousand</l>
<l>spoken by Caṭakōpaṉ, the king of Kurukai, man from the fertile land of Vaḻuti with serviceable groves</l>
<l>on the lord of the celestials who grants grace to all living being in the earth world,</l>
<l>being difficult to see for the eyes, being well easy for the intention,</l>
	<l>join as devotees, praise.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
